description: Allows a worker to assume a queue role.

parameters.name: farmId
parameters.description: The farm ID of the worker assuming the queue role.

parameters.name: fleetId
parameters.description: The fleet ID of the worker assuming the queue role.

parameters.name: workerId
parameters.description: The worker ID of the worker assuming the queue role.

parameters.name: queueId
parameters.description: The queue ID of the worker assuming the queue role.

nested_items.name: credentials
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services credentials for the role that the worker is assuming.

nested_items.name: expiration
nested_items.description: The expiration date and time of the IAM credentials.
